seekingalpha.com/symbol/DOL:CA\" title=\"Dollarama Inc.\">DOL:CA</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DLMAF\" title=\"Dollarama Inc.\">OTCPK:DLMAF</a>), Canada's not-quite equivalent chain of low-priced everyday items when compared against U.S. giants Dollar Tree (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DLTR\" title=\"Dollar Tree, Inc.\">DLTR</a>) and Dollar General (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1142952057/image_1142952057.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742517-dollarama-q3-the-veneer-loses-some-of-its-shine-management-comments-offer-hints", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 07:07:30"}, {"id": "4742515", "title": "Capital Southwest: Buying The Dip Despite Dividend Risks", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Excited Businessman Raises Hands and Punches Air while Celebrating Successful Deal. Stock Exchange Manager Happy After Investment Day. Broker in White Shirt Wins a Profitable Contract. Back View\" data-id=\"2045262949\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2045262949/image_2045262949.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_